column1: #text=I am more of a cook rather than a baker of pastries and sweets .
#text=But with the internet and youtube anything can be found .
#text=I searched youtube to find a good simple but interesting set of instructions .
#text=I decided on a chocolate cake as I am weak when it comes to resisting chocolate .
#text=I gathered all of the ingredients and placed them on the counter along with measuring cups and spoons .
#text=I could not believe how much sugar goes into the baking of a cake but that 's why it 's not a health food .
#text=All the ingredients went into a bowl for me to mix with a 1980 's hand held electric mixer .
#text=While the over was preheating I scooped a the mixture into a well greased baking pan .
#text=Naturally my finger stole a taste of the raw cake .
#text=After placing the bowl in the oven and and waiting the proper time I removed the cake and frosted it after it cooled down .
#text=Not too bad for a non baker but I 'll stick to cooking .
